  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the Lady of Horn Hill, see <a href=\"/index.php/Melessa_Florent\" title=\"Melessa Florent\">Melessa Florent</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Crakehall\" title=\"House Crakehall\"><img alt=\"House Crakehall.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/House_Crakehall.svg/50px-House_Crakehall.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/House_Crakehall.svg/75px-House_Crakehall.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a3/House_Crakehall.svg/100px-House_Crakehall.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Melesa Crakehall</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/50px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/75px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/100px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Melesa_Crakehall_by_dyannawynnedayne.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Melesa Crakehall by dyannawynnedayne.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/Melesa_Crakehall_by_dyannawynnedayne.jpg/350px-Melesa_Crakehall_by_dyannawynnedayne.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/Melesa_Crakehall_by_dyannawynnedayne.jpg/525px-Melesa_Crakehall_by_dyannawynnedayne.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9f/Melesa_Crakehall_by_dyannawynnedayne.jpg/700px-Melesa_Crakehall_by_dyannawynnedayne.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Melesa by dyannawynnedayne ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Crakehall\" title=\"House Crakehall\">House Crakehall</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey_of_Riverrun\" title=\"House Frey of Riverrun\">House Frey of Riverrun</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nSer <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Frey\" title=\"Lyonel Frey\">Lyonel Frey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Melesa Crakehall</b> is a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Crakehall\" title=\"House Crakehall\">House Crakehall</a> and the wife of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Frey\" title=\"Lyonel Frey\">Lyonel Frey</a>, the second son of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Emmon_Frey\" title=\"Emmon Frey\">Emmon Frey</a>, himself the second son of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a>. They have no progeny.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Her relation to the main Crakehalls is currently unknown. \n</p>\n<h2><span